      MultiResult Expect.expect(Matcher<?>... matchers)
      Blocks until all the given matchers match against the first input stream using the default timeout.
      MultiResult Expect.expectIn(int input, long timeoutMs, Matcher<?>... matchers)
      Deprecated.
